jobs.title: Statistics help: run K-Mode & Cramers V in Python
jobs.description: Hi there, I need your help with running a kmode and Cramer V analysis with existing test data using Python. A while ago I ran the analysis already, so I have the existing and working code already. Unfortunately, back then, the wrong input file was used (and does not exist anymore). So now I need to re-run the same analysis again, but on the correct data. The modules that were used, pandas (read_Excel, crosstab), scipy.stats, numpy. For clarity, I have attached the full script that had been used. What exists: - I have a new input file (Excel), only the original input file from back then is missing - I have the Python script already (see attached) What needs to be done: - You should run the script with the new input file and provide me with the results Required deliverable: - Cramers V values - Kmode values - Python script Timeline: April 9th Let me know if you have any questions. Happy to discuss in more detail. Thanks, Alex
